---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About VPNVerdict" description="Learn about VPNVerdict's mission, testing methodology, and editorial standards.">
  <article class="about">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <span class="current">About</span>
    </nav>

    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="page-label">About</span>
      <h1>Independent VPN testing<br/><em>you can trust.</em></h1>
      <div class="header-rule"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <section>
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>VPNVerdict exists to help you make informed decisions about VPN services. We provide independent, unbiased reviews and comparisons based on real-world testing and analysis.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>How We Test</h2>
        <p>Every VPN we review goes through a comprehensive testing process:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Speed tests</strong> across multiple server locations at different times of day</li>
          <li><strong>Security audits</strong> including DNS leak tests, WebRTC leak checks, and kill switch verification</li>
          <li><strong>Streaming tests</strong> with Netflix, Disney+, BBC iPlayer, and other major platforms</li>
          <li><strong>Usability evaluation</strong> across Windows, Mac, iOS, Android, and Linux</li>
          <li><strong>Privacy policy analysis</strong> reviewing logging practices, jurisdiction, and audit history</li>
          <li><strong>Value assessment</strong> comparing features, pricing, and simultaneous connection limits</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p>Our reviews are based on objective testing, not affiliate relationships. While we earn commissions when you purchase through our links, this never influences our ratings or recommendations. We recommend VPNs we'd use ourselves.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have questions, feedback, or a VPN you'd like us to review? Reach out at <a href="mailto:info@vpnverdict.net">info@vpnverdict.net</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-400); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--ink-500); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--ink-950); }
  .sep { color: var(--ink-300); }
  .current { color: var(--ink-400); }

  .page-header { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); animation: fadeInUp var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-400); }
  .page-header h1 { margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .page-header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-500); }
  .header-rule { height: 2px; width: 48px; background: var(--surface-inverse); }

  .content section { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .content h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); padding-top: var(--space-xl); border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100); }
  .content section:first-child h2 { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; }
  .content p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.75; }
  .content ul { color: var(--ink-700); }
  .content li { line-height: 1.75; }
  .contact a { font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
